		<p class="max-w-[42rem] leading-normal text-muted-foreground sm:text-xl sm:leading-8">
			Chat with our AI expert to learn how to deploy, monetize, and collaborate with AI agents in our decentralized marketplace.
		</p>
		<div class="space-x-4">
			<a href="/deploy"
				class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-md border-2 border-violet-600 text-violet-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium transition-colors hover:bg-violet-600 hover:text-white">
				Deploy Your Agent
